  "contents": "<div class=\"content markitup-box\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t习明泽给她土匪皇帝老爹习大马棒近平诞出<b>中国黑色接班人</b>：<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9wb21mMi5sYWluLmxhL2YvMnM5bnYwcDQuanBlZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://pomf2.lain.la/f/2s9nv0p4.jpeg\"><img alt=\"https://pomf2.lain.la/f/2s9nv0p4.jpeg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://pomf2.lain.la/f/2s9nv0p4.jpeg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<br/>\r\n习近平挥洒奴才血汗钱一掷千金喂养了那么多黑非洲“朋友”，也该养养自己屋里血缘的黑色革命后代啦。这习明泽与非洲酋长的爱情结晶就叫 “Howard • Xi • Edwards — 好耳朵•习•爱德华滋” 吧？不诞生多点黑黄爱国种儿，怎么对得起习大马棒挥霍无度的那些一戴一路金银财宝亿万钱财洒在黑非洲又强配华女给大批黑色“留学生”糟蹋啊🤔？攻打台湾中非黄黑敢死队一马当先！<br/>\n<br/>\r\n后人叹：<br/>\n<b>乱送金银求操</b><br/>\n<b>硬配黑子爱国</b><br/>\n<b>习家从此杂色</b><br/>\n<b>红色江山串种</b>。<br/>\n<br/>\n<b>古有昭君出塞</b><br/>\n<b>今见习女嫁黑</b><br/>\n<b>以前杂种在外</b><br/>\n<b>现在爱国混血。</b><br/>\n<br/>\n<b><a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/38242\" title=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/38242\">乱世笑林</a> <a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/58712\" title=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/58712\">解放军杂色犯台</a> <a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/60021\" title=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/60021\">黑色爱国增量</a> <a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/69349\" title=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/69349\">强把中国民女按到非洲黑子胯下</a></b> </div>",
